  "prompt": "I am an average student preparing for the IIT-JEE. Which test series is the best for me for free?",
  "response": "When preparing for IIT-JEE as an average student, it's important to choose the right test series that aligns with your preparation level and helps you improve. While there are many paid test series available, there are also some excellent free resources that you can utilize:\n\n### **Free Test Series for IIT-JEE Preparation:**\n\n1. **ETOOSINDIA Free Test Series**  \n   - Offers free test series for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n   - Provides detailed solutions and performance analysis.  \n   - Available on their website and app.  \n\n2. **Allen Career Institute Free Test Series**  \n   - Allen occasionally offers free tests for JEE aspirants.  \n   - Tests are designed to mimic the actual exam pattern.  \n   - Keep an eye on their official website and social media for updates.  \n\n3. **Unacademy JEE Free Mock Tests**  \n   - Unacademy offers free mock tests for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n   - Tests are designed by top educators and include detailed solutions.  \n   - Available on the Unacademy app and website.  \n\n4. **Vedantu JEE Free Test Series**  \n   - Vedantu provides free mock tests for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n   - Tests include performance analysis and solutions.  \n   - Accessible through the Vedantu app or website.  \n\n5. **Embibe JEE Free Test Series**  \n   - Embibe offers AI-based mock tests for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n   - Provides detailed analytics and personalized feedback.  \n   - Available on the Embibe app.  \n\n6. **Toppr JEE Free Test Series**  \n   - Toppr provides free mock tests for JEE Main.  \n   - Tests are designed to help students identify their strengths and weaknesses.  \n   - Accessible on the Toppr app or website.  \n\n7. **BYJU'S JEE Free Test Series**  \n   - BYJU'S offers free mock tests for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n   - Includes detailed solutions and performance analysis.  \n   - Available on the BYJU'S app and website.  \n\n8. **Physics Wallah (Alakh Pandey) Free Test Series**  \n   - PW offers free test series for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n   - Tests are designed by experienced educators and include detailed solutions.  \n   - Available on the PW app and website.  \n\n9. **Testbook JEE Free Test Series**  \n   - Testbook provides free mock tests for JEE Main.  \n   - Tests are designed to help students practice and improve their performance.  \n   - Accessible on the Testbook app or website.  \n\n10. **Doubtnut Free Test Series**  \n    - Doubtnut offers free mock tests for JEE Main and Advanced.  \n    - Tests include video solutions and performance analysis.  \n    - Available on the Doubtnut app.  \n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Using Free Test Series Effectively:**\n- **Analyze Your Performance:** After each test, thoroughly review your mistakes and understand the concepts behind them.  \n- **Track Your Progress:** Take tests regularly and track your performance to identify areas of improvement.  \n- **Simulate Exam Conditions:** Attempt tests in a timed environment to build speed and accuracy.  \n- **Combine with Study Material:** Use the test series alongside your regular study material to reinforce concepts.  \n\nThese free test series can be a great supplement to your preparation, but also focus on practicing from previous years' papers and NCERT for a strong foundation. Good luck with your JEE preparation!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
